name: Inside your Womb (Resides a Story. A Past Life)
description:
✦ 2nd Artwork for Obscure Delirium Series ✦

Obscure Delirium is a series made to capture the period in which one loses awareness of oneself and one's surroundings ✾

The more you know, the more you don't know
Seen too much, haven't seen enough
-
Once in a lifetime, we might wish to be reborn to rewrite the past and to change something in our life. We are but creatures trapped in the present time. However, as we go through life inside the womb of mother nature, a similar experience of feeling reborn as a completely different person can actually happen even just for once in our lifetime.
